  "body": "The Eth2.0 implementation teams have decided it's best off to define a deterministic sqrt helper function rather than the built in implementation for various languages. This is to reduce errors across implementations on consensus critical calculations which will be used by the rewards scheme. \r\n\r\nTo resolve this issue, we should implement the helper function mentioned [here](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/13) and use it in our casper package. ",
