    "body": "@nisdas You are missing the factor of 2 and the `B // reward_quotient` that is multiplied before the final division:\r\n```\r\nB // reward_quotient * (2 * total_participated_v_deposits - total_v_deposits) // total_v_deposits\r\n```\r\n\r\nFor normal ranges of B and `reward_quotient`,\r\n* when `total_participated_v_deposits` is > 50% of total_deposits this results in a positive number (reward)\r\n* when `total_participated_v_deposits` is < 50% of total_deposits this results in a negative number (penalty)\r\n* when `total_participated_v_deposits` is == 50% of total_deposits this results in 0.",
